Version                  Description
7.1.0   srand() has been made an alias of |mt_srand|.

===============================================================================
[ Examples ]

Example #1 srand() example

<?php >
  // seed with microseconds
  function make_seed()
  {
    list($usec, $sec) = explode(' ', microtime());
    return $sec + $usec * 1000000;
  }
  srand(make_seed());
  $randval = rand();
<?>

